article.description: — Ajare Sanni came off the bench to score 19 points to carry UC Santa Barbara to an 81-63 win over Cal State Fullerton on Friday.
article.headline: Sanni carries UC Santa Barbara past Cal St.-Fullerton 81-63
article.linkText: Sanni carries UC Santa Barbara past Cal St.-Fullerton 81-63
article.story: SANTA BARBARA, Calif. -- — Ajare Sanni came off the bench to score 19 points to carry UC Santa Barbara to an 81-63 win over Cal State Fullerton on Friday. JaQuori McLaughlin had 13 points and six assists for UC Santa Barbara (5-3, 1-2 Big West Conference), which earned its fourth straight home victory. Miles Norris added 13 points and three blocks. Amadou Sow had 12 points. Tray Maddox Jr. scored a career-high 27 points for the Titans (1-1, 0-1). Vincent Lee added 10 points.
